cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.CR

The paper deals with person re-identification, which is a subfield of computer vision. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely category. The paper also proposes a novel framework for person re-identification, which involves machine learning techniques, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) likely categories as well. The paper also deals with image and video processing, which falls under cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper discusses the robustness of the proposed technique to varying lighting conditions, which is a security concern, making cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) a possible category as well.
